item.dc:creator: @Sagi Sagi
item.description:
@Sagi wrote:

famoushope:

well i asked how to get compile code but no one tells me…?

I can help you, when you edit the compiling code.
You’ll have something like: “C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin”
change it to
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin\javac.exe”

Hope it works…
